creator: CanaryDroid
descriptionHtml:
Do you have what it takes to be crowned in the Wild West? Build your town, attack, revenge and steal your friends’ treasure, and explore a time when the Wild West was a new frontier.

Join millions of players worldwide as you spin the slots, build your clan and compete in epic online battles. Shall you live in the cowboys’ or the outlaws’ life?

West Clash Features:
- Attack your enemies or social network friends; just aim your cannon, fire and loot!
- Steal from other towns and making their treasure YOUR TREASURE
- Revenge on those who dare to attack your town
- Spin the wheel and master the slot of good fortune
- Build and upgrade your own town
- Battle against millions of players worldwide
- Invite Facebook friends to join the epic fun
- Collect new cowboy cards, and complete the album for even more epic game goodies
descriptionShort: Attack, revenge, steal your friends’ treasure and explore Wild West frontier!

container.value: Start Chambers, Wickham’s Cay II, P. O. Box 2221, Road Town, Tortola, British Virgin Island

creator: CanaryDroid
descriptionHtml:
Do you have what it takes to be crowned in the Wild West? Build your town, attack, revenge and steal your friends’ treasure, and explore a time when the Wild West was a new frontier.

Join millions of players worldwide as you spin the slots, build your clan and compete in epic online battles. Shall you live in the cowboys’ or the outlaws’ life?

West Clash Features:
- Attack your enemies or social network friends; just aim your cannon, fire and loot!
- Steal from other towns and making their treasure YOUR TREASURE
- Revenge on those who dare to attack your town
- Spin the wheel and master the slot of good fortune
- Build and upgrade your own town
- Battle against millions of players worldwide
- Invite Facebook friends to join the epic fun
- Collect new cowboy cards, and complete the album for even more epic game goodies
descriptionShort: Attack, revenge, steal your friends’ treasure and explore Wild West frontier!
